# AutoRise â€“ Smart Plant Watering Robot

## Description
**AutoRise** is a robot designed to water plants automatically based on soil moisture levels. It ensures healthy plant growth while saving time and water.

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- Soil Moisture Sensors  
- Water Pump  
- Python  

## Key Features
- Automatic plant watering  
- Soil moisture monitoring  
- Time-saving and efficient  

## My Role
Integrated sensors with pumps, programmed watering automation, and tested the system.

